OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FITV News' Anna Youssef has been
OL,7,Ffollowing Edwin Morrisons case.
OL,9,FA cash-strapped pensioner claimed he
OL,10,Ftried to rob a 95-year-old woman in
OL,11,Fher home to help pay for his own
OL,12,Ffuneral, a court has heard.
OL,14,FRetired pharmacy courier Edwin
OL,15,FMorrison, 81, strangled his victim as
OL,16,Fhe shouted, "give me your money" and
OL,17,Fthen bound her hands together with
OL,18,Fcable ties.
OL,26,@xD@MOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
