PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FHis victim pleaded with him to let her
OL,7,Fgo as she said she could not breathe,
OL,8,Fbut Morrison told her to "shut up".
OL,10,FMorrison only left empty-handed from
OL,11,Fthe property in Little Hulton,
OL,12,FSalford, as he was foiled by the
OL,13,Farrival of the woman's mobile
OL,14,Fhairdresser, Manchester Crown Court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FHe was said to have targeted his
OL,18,Fvulnerable victim after he visited her
OL,19,Fhome previously when delivering
OL,20,Fmedication as part of his former job.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
