PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FMorrison, who has no previous
OL,7,Fconvictions, retired aged 75 and was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with terminal kidney cancer
OL,9,Fin May 2024, the court heard.
OL,11,FProsecutors said Morrison, of Worsley,
OL,12,FGreater Manchester, was regularly
OL,13,Fgambling at his local bookmaker's in
OL,14,Fthe months before the attack on
OL,15,FJanuary 27 but did not visit the
OL,16,FBetfred shop on that day.
OL,18,FHe was also said to have expressed
OL,19,F"concerns" about funding a new kitchen
OL,20,Fat the home where he lived with his
OL,21,Flong-term partner.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FBut his lawyer said Morrison had
OL,7,Fgambled throughout his life and did
OL,8,Fnot hatch the robbery plan to pay off
OL,9,Fany debts.
OL,11,FA psychiatric report concluded he was
OL,12,Fsuffering from a "depressive
OL,13,Fdisorder", the court heard, by the end
OL,14,Fof 2025 and in a combination of
OL,15,F"depression and despair", he had
OL,16,Fdecided to end his life in February
OL,17,Fthis year while his partner was away
OL,18,Fon a break.
OL,26,@tD@ROUuD@IO]wD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
