PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FMorrison did not want to be a
OL,7,Ffinancial burden to his family in
OL,8,Fpaying for his funeral, said his
OL,9,Fbarrister Nick Clarke.
OL,11,FOn New Year's Day, he set up an online
OL,12,FGoFundMe appeal titled "Help to bury
OL,13,Fme" as he outlined his health problems.
OL,15,FHe wrote: "More or less been told to
OL,16,Fgo in a corner and see my time out. I
OL,17,Fhave no money to cover funeral costs
OL,18,Fand other incidentals."
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@CO]wD@KOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
