PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FMr Clarke told the court: "The
OL,7,FGoFundMe page was unsuccessful...so he
OL,8,Fcame up with this particular scheme,
OL,9,Fwhich in his mind would not be
OL,10,Fcomplicated and not cause the problems
OL,11,Fthat it did.
OL,13,F"He was utterly selfish and self-
OL,14,Fcentred ` for perhaps the first time
OL,15,Fin his life ` in committing this
OL,16,Foffence.
OL,26,@nD@[OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
