PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,F"He is remorseful for what he has
OL,7,Fdone. It is submitted that no real
OL,8,Fharm was intended. The motivation for
OL,9,Fthis offending was altruistic rather
OL,10,Fthan malicious."
OL,12,FHe said Morrison had, for the most
OL,13,Fpart of his life, been a loving
OL,14,Fpartner and a stepfather to a number
OL,15,Fof children and grandchildren.
OL,17,FMr Clarke added: "He was a working man
OL,18,Fwho delivered medicines for a pharmacy
OL,19,Fand he enjoyed the contact with
OL,20,Fmembers of the community."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]yD@ROU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
