PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FRob Smith, prosecuting, said Morrison
OL,7,Fwalked up the front path of his
OL,8,Fvictim's property at 11am after he
OL,9,Fparked his Peugeot car.
OL,11,FMorrison said he was there to inform
OL,12,Fher about a change in her bin
OL,13,Fcollection day and was invited into
OL,14,Fthe address.
OL,16,FShe later told police that they were
OL,17,Fsitting in her living room when "it
OL,18,Fall kicked off" when the defendant put
OL,19,Fhis hands around her throat as he
OL,20,Fdemanded cash.
OL,26,@yD@aOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
