PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement, she
OL,7,Ftold the court: "I thought I was going
OL,8,Fto die."
OL,10,FShortly after, mobile hairdresser
OL,11,FMichaela Nelson arrived for her weekly
OL,12,Fappointment and let herself in.
OL,14,FMr Smith said: "Ms Nelson went into
OL,15,Fthe lounge and saw an old man sitting
OL,16,Fin front of the victim and assumed he
OL,17,Fwas a friend.
OL,19,F"(The victim) shouted at her to call
OL,20,Fthe police and she at first thought it
OL,21,Fwas a joke."
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@HO]vD@POU{D@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
