PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FIn March, he pleaded guilty to a
OL,7,Fsingle count of attempted robbery.
OL,9,FThe prosecution asked for other
OL,10,Falleged offences of false imprisonment
OL,11,Fand intentional strangulation to lie
OL,12,Fon file.
OL,14,FJudge Peter Horgan adjourned the case
OL,15,Ffor a pre-sentence report to assess
OL,16,Fthe dangerousness of Morrison and to
OL,17,Ffind out more information about his
OL,18,Fhealth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
