SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773947499
OL,3,CElderly man tried to rob 95-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman to pay for funeral, court hears
OL,6,FHe told the defendant: "You know there
OL,7,Fwill be an immediate sentence of
OL,8,Fcustody in this case. The only
OL,9,Fquestion is how long."
OL,11,FMorrison was further remanded in
OL,12,Fcustody ahead of sentencing on April
OL,13,F15.
OL,26,@nD@XOUqD@VO]
